  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is the evaluation which is associated with apnea symptom, one of the recurrence factors,
      after AF ablation to patients who diagnosed AF.

      This is the evaluation which is associated with excessive respiration exercise during AF
      ablation to patients who diagnosed AF.

      This is the evaluation which is associated with excessive respiration exercise to make a gap
      during AF ablation to patients who diagnosed AF.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
